Package: EstemPMM
Type: Package
Title: Estimation with Polynomial Maximization Method (PMM)
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-01
Authors@R: 
    person("Serhii", "Zabolotnii", 
           email = "zabolotniua@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides an implementation of the polynomial maximization
  method for parameter estimation with non-Gaussian errors. Initially focusing on PMM2
  for linear (in parameters) models, but designed to be extended to other variations such
  as PMM3 in the future.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
